latestPosts.caption:
Reviewing the @paulaschoice 1% clinical retinol treatment - truly one of the best OTC retinoids I have ever tried! Retinol is one of the best ingredients for signs of aging, backed with the maximum scientific evidence (after sunscreens of course) and boy does this one pack in a punch! Definitely give it a go if you’re looking for something in the realm of retinoids but 🛑go slow!🛑 and maybe even layer it over a moisturizer the first couple times you use it just to be cautious! Trust me, this is strong!
